### Decorators

```python
import time

def timer(func):
    def wrapper(*args, **kwargs):
        start  = time.time()
        result = func(*args, **kwargs)
        print(f"{func.__name__} took {time.time() - start:.4f}s")
        return result
    return wrapper

@timer
def train(epochs):
    return sum(range(epochs))

train(1_000_000)
# train took 0.0342s
```

> 💡 Decorators are used heavily in **FastAPI** (`@app.get`), **PyTorch** (`@torch.no_grad()`), and **pytest** (`@pytest.fixture`)

